Popular Nigerian singer, Davido thanks his well wishers for the success of his trending new hit with Chris Brown “Blow My Mind” as he also slams his haters. Davido said he is used to the hate and nobody supports him since his 7 years in the music industry. Davido said he works hard, deliver hits, care for his people and he doesn’t care what people say about him He said: “I want to thank all my brothers, sisters and people that supported me including Chris. Me am already used to it, have been since 7 years and nobody supports me, its just hate because my papa get money, Naa my fault. I work hard, I deliver hits, I take care of my people. So if you gat a problem with me, Suck my dick, fuck you. We rise by lifting others. Gistvic Reports. Source